---
description:
Standards for forms and data entry.

alwaysApply: true
---

# Forms

Forms should be:

Simple

Guided

Forgiving

Accessible

---

# Validation

Validate progressively.

Avoid validating before interaction.

---

# Errors

Display errors inline.

Explain how to fix them.

---

# Labels

Every field has:

Label

Helper text (optional)

Validation

---

# Keyboard

Use appropriate keyboard types.

Support autofill.

---

# Buttons

Disable submit only when necessary.

Show loading during submission.

---

# Cursor Instructions

Forms should reduce friction.

Never overwhelm users.